pysyte.types.python
===================


    >>> from pysyte.streams import std


Doctest normally shows all streams

    >>> std.out("Hello")
    >>> std.err("World")
    Hello
    World

Suppress stderr
    >>> with quietly as fred:
    ...     std.out("Hello")
    ...     std.err("World")
    ...
    Hello

    >>> assert "World" in fred.stderr

Suppress stdout
    >>> with Quietly:
    ...     std.out("Hello")
    ...     std.err("World")
    ...
    World

Suppress both
    >>> with QUIETLY as fred:
    ...     std.out("Hello")
    ...     std.err("World")
    ...

Suppressed streams were stored in attributes

    >>> assert "Hello" in fred.stdout
    >>> assert "World" in fred.stderr

